    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Dear Molly,</p>
<p>There are times when all we can hope for is to truly comprehend that even when someone is gone, trivial and cliche as it may sound, that someone could never be truly dead for as long as we speak of them, think of them and know, without needing to believe in the afterlife that indeed we will see each other again. </p>
<p>I am so very sorry for your family&#39;s and your own personal loss.</p>
