      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">cottonjens</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2012/06/she-felt-like-cheering/#comment-32983"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2012-06-10T15:10:37-04:00">Sunday, June 10, 2012 at 3:10 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hang on. advice from my mother in law who knew this subject well. I have hung on since my mother passed 6 months ago. I doubted I could get thru it. she is no longer here to see or touch or talk to. my loss has been greatly soothed by my faith and love.</p>
    </div>

      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
