      <p>I understand completely the feeling of not knowing how or what to write about something so heavy.  The internet does seem somewhat awkward, except that there are readers who have or will go through something very similar.  What you shared gives a glimpse of how sweet your aunt was and your willingness to open up and share is appreciated.</p>
    </div>

