    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;m so sorry for your loss. This news hits close to home: my dad was diagnosed with pancreatic cancer las August and passes away in April. It took the life out of him very quickly and it was devastating to watch. I was pregnant at he time and he never got to meet my daughter. Like you, I was hesitant to talk about it on my blog, but I did and I&#39;m so grateful for the support I received. Thinking of you.</p>
    </div>

