    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thank you for sharing with us.  I think we who are left are here to be a witness, to spread word of what we loved about those who are no longer with us and to try to model what we learned from them.  Your first book helped me to learn to do that for my dad who I lost in much the same way you lost yours.  I gave a copy to my sister, not so much for the recipes since she&#39;s a vegetarian, but for the story that mirrored ours.  So sharing has power to help heal &#8211; I hope that healing comes back to you.</p>
    </div>

